# -*-perl-*-

=head1 NAME

_MAKE_MOSAIC_FRAME_ - Create frame mosaic

=head1 SYNOPSIS

 _MAKE_MOSAIC_FRAME_

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This primitive takes all the aligned sub-scan frames from each sub-array
and mosaics them into a single output image.

=head1 KNOWN ISSUES

Assumes the _ALIGN_ARRAYS_ primitive has been run on the input images.

=head1 ALGORITHMS

Usess CCDPACK MAKEMOS. This primitive is currently a very general
implementation.

=head1 FILE SUFFIX

Creates a single output image with a suffix of '_mos'.

